rows.label: tlk42350162_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Ah, that was scary, mo!
I thought I was going to die, mo!

rows.label: tlk42350162_01_msg0002
rows.name:
I was trying to go to Iyasaki Village
to do some business, but...

rows.label: tlk42350162_01_msg0003
rows.name:
I slipped on a narrow path on the way
and fell into the Cloud Sea, mo!

rows.label: tlk42350162_01_msg0004
rows.name:
I somehow managed to reach a small island
with the Noppy-paddle, but it was tough
climbing up from there, mo.

rows.label: tlk42350162_01_msg0005
rows.name:
You all are big, so you're probably more likely
to slip off than Esasa, mo.
Watch your step, mo!
